  "title": "The Time-Course of Food Representation in the Human Brain",
  "description": "This dataset contains raw EEG recordings investigating the temporal dynamics of food representation in the human brain. The study employs electroencephalography to characterize how food-related information is processed and represented across different time windows during neural processing. The data are organized in BIDS format to facilitate reproducibility and secondary analysis.",
